{"tid":567159,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"OpenRice多打手文 CEO：公司有嚴格把關","createTime":"2018-02-20T15:12:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-15T10:53:14.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1318e1d3684d442cdd2fdbdd2a6b10384af51889","tid":567159,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180220/large/1519106502_16a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519106502_16a7.jpg&h=b67898e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《信報》引述OpenRice行政總裁邱桂雄表示，不甘於只做一個廣告及資訊平台，應用程式除了提供飲食資訊「幫人開飯」外，企業版OpenRice Biz其中一項重要新功能是提供招聘資訊，將進一步助人開工。<br />\n<br />\n邱桂雄指「其實餐飲業的員工流失率很高，打工仔很多時未必知道（邊度）有工（搵）」。OpenRice Biz較其他招聘平台優勝之處，在於餐廳之間會經常留意其他行家的情況，OpenRice自然是業界其中一個重要的資訊平台。<br />\n<br />\n多年來均有人指平台內的食評有「打手文」或抹黑餐廳的問題。他則坦言公司在審批評論時嚴格把關，更會提醒消費者在撰寫批評的文章時，內容必須屬實，否則可能會面對來自餐廳的法律訴訟，並指「已說了很多遍，在OpenRice是不能買食評。」，同時會向用戶解釋評論遭刪除的理由，以提高透明度。<br />\n<br />\nOpenRice今年初獲里巴巴旗下螞蟻金服入股，成功「泊得大碼頭」，邱桂雄表明仍以香港市場為主，又指應用程式每日有數十萬個活躍用戶，下載用戶更有500多萬戶，流量相當充足。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180220/57852699\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57852699&d=LG5iZRcf1akFTiRMjndvrTACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=119c4b54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180220%2F57852699&h=62bded8a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180220/57852699</a><br />\n<br />\n人唔笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b40664a50311ba31fa90f1b1086e1c48631ab9","tid":567159,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"同醫生網一樣,無錢俾就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c600560e54e099c50e3ecfff7eae0f25aa6858","tid":567159,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T12:02:39.000Z","msg":"講出嚟自己都未必信啦"},{"pid":"b25e544235b2d0a122bcad0546387772d2765638","tid":567159,"uid":46493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T10:53:14.000Z","msg":"無你老母，係openrice試過幾間勁多好評既伏撚到仆街，每次食完嬲嬲豬出負評post都出唔撚到，唔撚係收左錢我真係唔信lo<br />\n<br />\n識朋友做openrice打手，專寫好評，咁撚樣都叫無？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}